sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ExtProc as Payload Processing<br/>9004/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant ModelRes as model-provider-resolver<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant APITrans as api-translation<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant APIKey as apikey-injection<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant NemoGrd as nemo-request-guard<br/>(optional plugin)
    participant NemoSvc as NeMo Guardrails<br/>Service
    participant Provider as External AI Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request Pipeline

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user)<br/>Body: OpenAI format
    Gateway->>ExtProc: ext_proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9004 (pod-local, plaintext)

    Note over ExtProc: body-field-to-header extracts<br/>model name → X-Gateway-Model-Name

    ExtProc->>ModelRes: RequestProcess()
    Note over ModelRes: Reads modelInfoStore (in-memory)<br/>Pre-cached via ExternalModel reconciler
    ModelRes-->>ExtProc: CycleState: provider, targetModel, credRef

    ExtProc->>APITrans: RequestProcess()
    Note over APITrans: Reads CycleState.ProviderName<br/>Translates OpenAI → provider format<br/>(Anthropic, Vertex, Azure, Bedrock)
    APITrans-->>ExtProc: Mutated body + headers<br/>Strips original Authorization header

    ExtProc->>APIKey: RequestProcess()
    Note over APIKey: Reads CycleState.CredentialRef<br/>Reads secretStore (in-memory)<br/>Injects provider-specific auth header
    APIKey-->>ExtProc: Added auth header<br/>(Bearer / x-api-key / api-key)

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: ext_proc ProcessingResponse<br/>Mutated headers + body

    Gateway->>Provider: Forwarded request<br/>Provider-native format<br/>Auth: Injected API key
    Provider-->>Gateway: Provider-native response

    Gateway->>ExtProc: ext_proc ProcessingRequest (response phase)
    ExtProc->>APITrans: ResponseProcess()
    Note over APITrans: Translates provider response<br/>→ OpenAI format
    APITrans-->>ExtProc: Translated response body
    ExtProc-->>Gateway: ext_proc ProcessingResponse

    Gateway-->>Client: OpenAI-format response

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: NeMo Guardrails Check (Optional - when enabled)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>ExtProc: ext_proc ProcessingRequest
    ExtProc->>NemoGrd: RequestProcess()
    NemoGrd->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/rails/check<br/>Body: last user message<br/>Timeout: 360s
    NemoSvc-->>NemoGrd: Rail evaluation result
    alt Rails pass
        NemoGrd-->>ExtProc: Continue pipeline
    else Rails block
        NemoGrd-->>ExtProc: Return error (blocked)
        ExtProc-->>Gateway: Error response
        Gateway-->>Client: 400/403 Blocked by guardrails
    end

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 3: Background Reconciliation (async, continuous)

    loop ExternalModel Reconciler
        ModelRes->>ModelRes: Watch ExternalModel CRDs<br/>via controller-runtime
        Note over ModelRes: K8s API 443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        ModelRes->>ModelRes: Update modelInfoStore
    end

    loop Secret Reconciler
        APIKey->>APIKey: Watch labeled Secrets<br/>(bbr-managed=true)
        Note over APIKey: K8s API 443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        APIKey->>APIKey: Update secretStore
    end
